# --- Terraform live-run: ignore heavy/transient, KEEP all logs + plan renderings ---
# Provider binaries (~hundreds of MB) and local state are transient, not evidence.
live-run/.terraform/
live-run/.terraform.lock.hcl
live-run/terraform.tfstate
live-run/terraform.tfstate.*
live-run/evidence/tfplan.binary
# NOTE: deliberately NOT ignored (these ARE the evidence and must be tracked):
#   live-run/logs/*.log
#   live-run/evidence/plan_readable.txt
#   live-run/evidence/plan.json
#   live-run/main.tf, live-run/*.ps1
